WEBVTT

01:52.259 --> 01:52.940
Lawyer Xu,

01:53.380 --> 01:54.380
I've checked everything.

01:54.660 --> 01:55.660
Nothing's missing.

01:56.380 --> 01:56.780
Good.

01:57.660 --> 01:58.780
I'm done packing up.

01:59.059 --> 01:59.940
I'll be on my way.

02:02.819 --> 02:03.500
Lawyer Xu,

02:04.500 --> 02:06.500
thank you for today.

02:08.339 --> 02:09.140
Don't overthink it.

02:09.619 --> 02:10.500
Get a good night's sleep.

02:21.859 --> 02:23.139
No more phone at night.

02:27.699 --> 02:28.259
Good night.

02:29.620 --> 02:30.259
[Good night.]

02:46.699 --> 02:48.100
Where does he usually sleep?

02:52.739 --> 02:55.019
Anyway, the sheets are new.

02:56.139 --> 02:58.419
Just pretend I'm in a hotel.

03:13.859 --> 03:14.380
Hello?

03:15.900 --> 03:16.419
Hello?

03:16.579 --> 03:17.460
Ruan Yu, are you okay?

03:18.660 --> 03:19.660
I'm fine.

03:21.539 --> 03:23.380
You... you didn't reply.

03:23.380 --> 03:24.060
I was worried.

03:24.940 --> 03:25.780
Glad you're okay.

03:26.419 --> 03:27.100
That's good.

03:27.780 --> 03:28.539
Sorry,

03:28.539 --> 03:29.940
I was washing up and didn't see it.

03:33.699 --> 03:34.460
So,

03:35.460 --> 03:36.940
are you with Lawyer Xu?

03:39.019 --> 03:41.579
Is Lawyer Xu

03:41.579 --> 03:42.979
still with you?

03:43.979 --> 03:44.460
No,

03:44.460 --> 03:45.419
he went to the hotel.

03:47.819 --> 03:48.819
Are you looking for Lawyer Xu

03:48.819 --> 03:49.579
for something?

03:53.220 --> 03:53.660
No,

03:54.419 --> 03:55.940
I just thought of

03:55.940 --> 03:57.139
a legal question

03:57.139 --> 03:57.940
I wanted to ask him.

03:58.340 --> 03:58.979
It's fine if he's not here.

03:59.180 --> 03:59.859
It's fine.

03:59.979 --> 04:00.859
I have his WeChat.

04:01.579 --> 04:03.139
If you have any questions,

04:03.419 --> 04:04.340
I can send him a message

04:04.340 --> 04:04.819
and ask.

04:05.100 --> 04:05.579
No need.

04:07.100 --> 04:07.539
No need.

04:08.139 --> 04:09.100
Get some rest.

04:09.620 --> 04:10.180
Take care.

04:10.699 --> 04:11.259
Bye.

04:27.859 --> 04:28.700
Lawyer Xu,

04:28.939 --> 04:30.619
I'll cover your hotel bill tonight.

04:32.059 --> 04:32.859
No need for that.

04:33.499 --> 04:34.179
Get some rest.

04:40.179 --> 04:40.820
I'll be up late,

04:41.220 --> 04:42.220
so call me if you need anything.

04:48.859 --> 04:49.379
Good night.

04:51.979 --> 04:52.939
[Xu Huaisong]

04:53.140 --> 04:54.820
[actually says good night to someone?]

04:57.179 --> 04:57.739
[Good night.]

05:00.979 --> 05:01.419
[Sleep tight.]

05:03.539 --> 05:04.820
[His instant reply]

05:05.379 --> 05:06.939
[is like a perfect male lead]

05:07.260 --> 05:08.820
[who never lets a girl end a conversation]

05:08.820 --> 05:09.979
[in a novel.]

05:12.419 --> 05:13.700
[Is this aloof guy]

05:14.660 --> 05:15.820
[possessed today?]

05:18.820 --> 05:19.900
[Stop overthinking.]

06:41.179 --> 06:42.179
[Lawyer Xu,]

06:43.700 --> 06:45.140
[do you have any fever medicine at home?]

06:51.059 --> 06:51.739
Who is it?

06:57.100 --> 06:57.739
Who is it?

06:58.660 --> 06:59.859
Ruan Yu, it's me.

07:02.299 --> 07:03.539
Lawyer Xu, what are you doing here?

07:04.059 --> 07:04.979
I'm still worried about you.

07:07.739 --> 07:08.419
It's nothing serious.

07:08.700 --> 07:09.700
Actually, you could have just

07:09.739 --> 07:11.059
told me where the medicine is.

07:11.859 --> 07:12.739
I brought some extra.

07:15.220 --> 07:15.859
You're burning up.

07:16.900 --> 07:17.780
It's nothing serious.

07:18.499 --> 07:19.460
Just sit on the couch.

07:20.260 --> 07:20.820
Okay.

07:31.059 --> 07:31.660
Come on.

07:32.140 --> 07:33.260
Let me take your temperature first.

07:37.739 --> 07:38.780
39 degrees.

07:39.820 --> 07:40.939
I should take you to the hospital.

07:43.379 --> 07:43.979
No need.

07:43.979 --> 07:44.979
It's so late.

07:45.260 --> 07:46.780
I should take some medicine

07:46.780 --> 07:47.739
and get some sleep.

07:48.020 --> 07:48.979
Besides the fever,

07:48.979 --> 07:49.979
do you have any other discomfort?

07:52.619 --> 07:53.700
My throat hurts a bit.

07:54.020 --> 07:55.379
I feel a bit cold.

07:55.660 --> 07:56.419
That's all.

07:58.059 --> 07:58.619
Come on.

07:59.660 --> 08:00.660
Cover yourself with a blanket.

08:01.580 --> 08:02.379
Thank you.

08:03.499 --> 08:04.619
I'll get you some hot water.

08:30.260 --> 08:30.739
Here.

08:32.179 --> 08:32.739
Thank you.

08:39.460 --> 08:40.820
Take some fever-reducing medicine.

08:41.379 --> 08:41.820
Here.

08:49.460 --> 08:50.220
Drink more water.

08:50.540 --> 08:51.659
I'll make you some medicine.

09:31.659 --> 09:32.139
Ruan Yu.

09:33.940 --> 09:34.460
Ruan Yu.

09:40.300 --> 09:41.300
Take the medicine first.

09:54.700 --> 09:55.700
Come on, wake up.

09:56.300 --> 09:56.940
Take the medicine.

10:20.259 --> 10:20.779
Ruan Yu.

10:23.739 --> 10:24.180
Come on.

10:24.899 --> 10:25.700
Take the medicine first.

10:30.580 --> 10:31.060
Come on.

10:40.420 --> 10:41.820
Take another sip.

11:09.060 --> 11:10.460
I want to carry you back to the room.

11:11.540 --> 11:12.019
Is that okay?

12:20.060 --> 12:21.460
What kind of love potion?

12:22.820 --> 12:23.820
Don't talk nonsense.

12:33.300 --> 12:34.220
I've already

12:37.139 --> 12:38.379
[for a long time.]

13:17.420 --> 13:18.379
[Could you]

13:20.420 --> 13:21.580
[fall in love with me again?]

14:34.060 --> 14:35.060
Where are my shoes?

14:58.340 --> 14:59.060
Morning, Lawyer Xu.

14:59.859 --> 15:00.460
You're up.

15:09.180 --> 15:10.100
Why aren't you wearing shoes?

15:12.139 --> 15:13.300
I... I couldn't find

15:13.499 --> 15:14.379
my shoes in the room.

15:15.940 --> 15:16.540
Wait a moment.

15:25.619 --> 15:27.259
The slippers are by the sofa.

15:27.700 --> 15:28.820
So yesterday was...

15:29.580 --> 15:30.420
Put on your shoes first.

15:33.859 --> 15:34.659
Thank you, Lawyer Xu.

15:36.460 --> 15:37.499
Thank you for

15:37.899 --> 15:39.060
carrying me in yesterday.

15:39.619 --> 15:40.659
You are a writer.

15:41.460 --> 15:42.820
You know how to use words.

15:43.460 --> 15:44.100
You're welcome.

15:46.739 --> 15:47.499
Take your temperature again.

15:54.820 --> 15:55.340
Sit.

16:10.619 --> 16:12.540
Lawyer Xu, this is...

16:13.859 --> 16:14.499
The research report

16:14.499 --> 16:15.859
on the effect of antipyretics.

16:19.499 --> 16:20.019
Do you believe it?

16:26.700 --> 16:27.659
I'll go wash up first.

16:28.180 --> 16:28.580
Okay.

16:45.580 --> 16:47.379
I can't live like this.

16:47.899 --> 16:49.300
I need to find a house to move out.

16:52.460 --> 16:53.779
Mingying, do you have

16:53.779 --> 16:54.580
any reliable housing options?

16:55.019 --> 16:55.940
I want to rent a house

16:55.940 --> 16:56.499
for a transition.

17:00.460 --> 17:01.180
Last night,

17:01.180 --> 17:02.340
weren't you still living comfortably

17:02.340 --> 17:03.259
at Xu Huaisong's place?

17:03.820 --> 17:04.779
Are you worried about

17:04.779 --> 17:05.820
yourself and him?

17:06.820 --> 17:08.820
My dear friend, please help me.

17:11.019 --> 17:12.459
Alright, I'll help you.

17:12.540 --> 17:13.540
I'll let you know if I find anything.

17:20.980 --> 17:22.419
Chuan.

17:23.340 --> 17:24.379
Are you busy?

17:25.419 --> 17:27.459
Yeah, I'm busy with product selection.

17:28.619 --> 17:30.300
You've been looking at your phone a lot.

17:30.659 --> 17:32.020
Is your shoulder uncomfortable?

17:32.419 --> 17:33.500
And your neck was sore yesterday.

17:37.300 --> 17:37.820
Chuan.

17:39.939 --> 17:41.179
lend me your ID card.

17:42.699 --> 17:44.139
What do you need it for?

17:46.859 --> 17:50.379
To get our marriage certificate, of course.

17:54.260 --> 17:55.379
Haven't you heard?

17:55.379 --> 17:56.379
You can get it

17:56.379 --> 17:57.740
without a household register now.

18:02.859 --> 18:03.820
Go get it.

18:04.580 --> 18:05.740
Alright, I'll get it for you.

18:06.060 --> 18:06.980
Hurry up.

18:20.659 --> 18:22.020
Hurry, give it to me.

18:30.020 --> 18:30.540
Hello?

18:30.859 --> 18:31.300
[Hello,]

18:31.379 --> 18:32.939
[Is this Mr. Zhang Chuan?]

18:33.379 --> 18:34.060
Yes, who's this?

18:34.780 --> 18:35.619
[Hello, Mr. Zhang.]

18:35.939 --> 18:37.340
[This is the front desk of Dacheng Hotel.]

18:37.820 --> 18:39.139
[You haven't checked out]

18:39.139 --> 18:40.020
[from room 602 yet.]

18:42.699 --> 18:43.580
I'm not buying a house.

18:46.580 --> 18:47.820
Too many scam calls.

18:48.139 --> 18:49.260
Yeah, there are

18:49.260 --> 18:50.340
a lot of scams lately.

18:50.340 --> 18:51.780
You should download an anti-fraud app.

18:53.419 --> 18:54.379
Alright, I'm heading to work.

18:55.379 --> 18:56.219
Bye.

19:01.260 --> 19:01.939
[Miss Shen,]

19:02.260 --> 19:03.540
[can you come to inspect the car this afternoon?]

19:29.419 --> 19:29.980
Hello, honey.

19:29.980 --> 19:30.580
Where are you?

19:31.580 --> 19:32.379
I just finished showering

19:32.699 --> 19:33.980
and getting ready to go to the office.

19:34.619 --> 19:36.300
The hotel front desk

19:36.300 --> 19:37.260
just called me,

19:37.260 --> 19:38.340
saying you haven't checked out.

19:38.780 --> 19:40.060
I'm worried something happened to you.

19:40.419 --> 19:42.300
I'm fine. See you at the office in a bit.

19:43.219 --> 19:43.899
See you later.

19:50.219 --> 19:50.780
Hello?

19:51.100 --> 19:51.699
[Hello.]

19:51.699 --> 19:53.260
[Is this Mr. Zhang Chuan?]

19:53.580 --> 19:54.300
Yes, who's this?

19:54.899 --> 19:55.820
[Hello, Mr. Zhang.]

19:56.100 --> 19:57.459
[This is the front desk of Dacheng Hotel.]

19:57.939 --> 19:59.340
[You haven't checked out]

19:59.340 --> 20:00.100
[from Room 602 yet.]

20:01.619 --> 20:02.419
I'm not buying a house.

20:04.580 --> 20:05.820
Too many scams.

20:31.780 --> 20:32.419
Last night,

20:45.020 --> 20:45.780
[did you wake up?]

20:46.859 --> 20:47.820
[How's your stay]

20:47.820 --> 20:48.580
[at Lawyer Xu's?]

20:50.379 --> 20:51.139
Lawyer Xu.

20:51.219 --> 20:52.179
I'll check my WeChat.

20:57.899 --> 20:58.619
I'm doing well.

20:58.619 --> 20:59.340
Don't worry.

21:00.179 --> 21:00.820
As for the legal issue

21:00.899 --> 21:02.619
you mentioned yesterday,

21:02.619 --> 21:03.419
is it serious?

21:03.859 --> 21:05.060
I'll ask for you.

21:09.740 --> 21:11.020
No need, it's already been resolved.

21:13.859 --> 21:15.619
What are your plans for today?

21:17.419 --> 21:18.500
I'm going to look for an apartment.

21:20.020 --> 21:20.859
Are you thinking of moving?

21:21.419 --> 21:23.340
Yeah, I don't know when

21:23.340 --> 21:24.340
Cen Sisi's case

21:24.340 --> 21:25.260
will be completely resolved.

21:25.740 --> 21:26.580
I shouldn't keep

21:26.580 --> 21:27.899
bothering Lawyer Xu.

21:28.139 --> 21:28.899
So I think

21:28.899 --> 21:29.780
it would be more convenient

21:29.780 --> 21:30.459
to move to another apartment.

21:30.699 --> 21:31.459
Leave it to me.

21:31.659 --> 21:32.340
I'll help you find a new place.

21:32.540 --> 21:33.619
I'll get it done for you within a day.

21:37.260 --> 21:38.540
No need to rush.

21:41.020 --> 21:41.619
You...

21:42.939 --> 21:44.100
You're with Lawyer Xu.

21:56.100 --> 21:56.939
Let's go eat first.

21:57.179 --> 21:57.740
It's getting cold.

22:20.780 --> 22:21.899
The custard buns are still warm.

22:22.260 --> 22:23.260
Come on, try some.

22:25.780 --> 22:26.340
No need.

22:29.659 --> 22:30.859
I'm fine, I'll do it myself.

22:37.459 --> 22:38.500
Why are you blushing?

22:39.060 --> 22:39.980
Are you having a fever again?

22:50.500 --> 22:51.340
You have a fever?

22:52.100 --> 22:52.580
No, no.

22:52.939 --> 22:53.740
I'm fine today

22:53.740 --> 22:54.659
after what happened yesterday.

23:00.179 --> 23:01.419
Have you been to the hospital?

23:01.699 --> 23:02.340
I'll take you there.

23:05.980 --> 23:06.580
No need.

23:07.060 --> 23:08.820
You heard her. No need.

23:10.740 --> 23:11.699
Don't be so polite to me.

23:11.980 --> 23:12.899
I'm not.

23:13.219 --> 23:14.740
I just feel almost well.

23:17.820 --> 23:18.340
Take your time.

23:18.780 --> 23:19.459
Have some milk.

23:50.740 --> 23:51.780
You can take it home.

23:51.780 --> 23:52.260
Thanks.

23:52.260 --> 23:52.820
Okay.

24:00.459 --> 24:00.820
Come on.

24:02.379 --> 24:03.139
Do you think

24:03.619 --> 24:04.899
it's an infringement

24:04.899 --> 24:06.060
of my privacy

24:06.740 --> 24:08.139
to disclose my exam results?

24:11.260 --> 24:13.459
Monthly quiz again?

24:14.459 --> 24:15.780
Today is gift exchange day.

24:16.379 --> 24:17.020
What did you give

24:17.020 --> 24:17.899
to the Ministry of Culture and Entertainment?

24:20.740 --> 24:22.780
Don't hide it. I know it all.

24:23.859 --> 24:24.659
What do you know?

24:25.139 --> 24:26.139
I know your little tricks.

24:26.139 --> 24:27.139
You can't hide it from me.

24:27.899 --> 24:28.500
Give it to me.

24:29.980 --> 24:30.740
Give what?

24:31.100 --> 24:32.379
Come on. Let's go to eat.

24:34.740 --> 24:36.060
I'm telling you.

24:36.419 --> 24:38.020
As friends,

24:38.020 --> 24:39.419
what don't I know about you?

24:40.060 --> 24:41.740
We are all in the age of 17 or 18,

24:41.740 --> 24:42.859
and just start to fall in love.

24:42.859 --> 24:43.659
Don't talk nonsense.

24:43.939 --> 24:45.340
I'm not.

24:46.740 --> 24:48.100
Fine, you don't admit it.

24:48.780 --> 24:49.419
Then let me ask you,

24:49.939 --> 24:50.740
why

24:50.859 --> 24:51.820
you are normal

24:51.820 --> 24:52.699
with others

24:52.899 --> 24:53.780
these days,

24:54.060 --> 24:55.340
but just feel awkward

24:55.340 --> 24:56.260
with me?

24:56.899 --> 24:57.780
You're not normal.

25:04.820 --> 25:05.659
Fine.

25:07.859 --> 25:09.060
I'll tell you.

25:10.419 --> 25:11.699
Look, someone wrote you a love letter.

25:11.699 --> 25:12.540
It's not a big deal.

25:15.260 --> 25:16.020
A love letter?

25:19.340 --> 25:20.020
Go away.

25:20.939 --> 25:22.139
Zhao Yi, what are you doing?

25:22.139 --> 25:23.780
Just tell me.

25:23.780 --> 25:24.820
Which class is that girl from?

25:24.820 --> 25:25.820
Do I know her?

25:26.020 --> 25:26.939
Don't be so nosy.

25:26.939 --> 25:28.659
Just tell me.

25:28.780 --> 25:29.219
Zhao Yi.

25:31.820 --> 25:32.699
Xu Huai Shi, I'm telling you,

25:32.699 --> 25:33.580
this is my personal privacy.

25:34.300 --> 25:35.060
I'm just concerned about your

25:35.060 --> 25:35.820
personal life.

25:36.060 --> 25:36.740
Principal.

25:38.260 --> 25:38.820
Zhao Yi.

25:39.540 --> 25:39.899
Come here.

25:41.379 --> 25:42.379
You come back here.

25:49.580 --> 25:50.699
You...

25:52.340 --> 25:53.219
The back door is locked.

25:53.219 --> 25:54.300
You can only get out by climbing over the wall.

25:54.540 --> 25:55.419
If you can get out,

25:55.419 --> 25:56.100
you're good.

25:56.379 --> 25:56.780
You...

25:57.060 --> 25:58.219
Don't look down on me.

25:58.219 --> 25:58.899
I'm telling you.

26:01.340 --> 26:01.820
Go.

26:04.859 --> 26:05.419
You hold me.

26:06.060 --> 26:07.899
I hold you, do you hold me?

26:08.260 --> 26:09.340
I'll count to three.

26:10.459 --> 26:10.899
One.

26:11.939 --> 26:12.459
Two.

26:14.659 --> 26:15.540
Don't bother me when I'm eating.

26:17.020 --> 26:17.740
So annoying.

26:18.340 --> 26:19.419
Don't be mad.

26:28.060 --> 26:29.139
You just recovered from a fever.

26:29.580 --> 26:30.619
It's not too late to look for a house

26:30.619 --> 26:31.300
a few days later.

26:32.980 --> 26:33.899
I'll just see

26:40.020 --> 26:40.740
if there's anything suitable.

26:42.139 --> 26:42.820
I just looked at a few.

26:42.820 --> 26:43.500
They're not bad.

26:45.619 --> 26:46.060
Really?

26:46.820 --> 26:47.899
Then let me help you decide.

26:51.500 --> 26:52.500
from a lawyer's perspective.

27:06.980 --> 27:07.659
Hey, sir.

27:08.219 --> 27:09.500
What are you doing?

27:10.379 --> 27:11.859
I just threw something away.

27:11.980 --> 27:12.820
Did you see it?

27:12.859 --> 27:13.980
I'll take what I pick up.

27:13.980 --> 27:14.939
Why are you grabbing it?

27:15.619 --> 27:16.939
What are you talking about?

27:24.899 --> 27:25.699
What are you doing?

27:26.820 --> 27:27.139
You...

27:35.580 --> 27:36.699
This is what I want.

27:37.580 --> 27:38.419
This is the Great Writer's

27:38.419 --> 27:39.740
from the famous writer.

27:41.340 --> 27:43.540
But it can't fill my stomach.

27:43.580 --> 27:45.100
I need money.

27:45.179 --> 27:45.820
Silly girl.

27:47.859 --> 27:48.859
Silly girl.

27:51.980 --> 27:52.859
This house

27:52.939 --> 27:53.859
is too old.

27:54.300 --> 27:54.780
Look,

27:54.899 --> 27:56.500
the pipes in the bathroom

27:56.820 --> 27:57.580
and kitchen

27:57.580 --> 27:58.379
are in bad shape.

27:58.699 --> 27:59.540
You may encounter

27:59.540 --> 28:00.540
you may encounter

28:00.659 --> 28:01.699
some issues during maintenance and replacement.

28:04.379 --> 28:05.179
The name

28:05.699 --> 28:06.300
of the agent

28:06.300 --> 28:07.859
and the property owner

28:07.859 --> 28:08.459
are different.

28:08.580 --> 28:09.699
It's likely a sublandlord.

28:09.820 --> 28:10.379
If a sublandlord

28:10.379 --> 28:11.820
has a contract dispute

28:11.820 --> 28:13.100
with the original owner,

28:13.179 --> 28:13.899
your rights

28:13.899 --> 28:15.179
will not be protected.

28:42.139 --> 28:42.780
This one...

28:43.740 --> 28:44.340
Lawyer Xu,

28:44.780 --> 28:45.619
I think this one

28:45.780 --> 28:46.619
doesn't have any of the issues

28:46.619 --> 28:47.379
you mentioned earlier.

28:48.260 --> 28:48.899
I've decided,

28:49.459 --> 28:50.100
this is the one.

28:50.340 --> 28:51.060
Don't rush.

28:51.419 --> 28:52.179
Let me take a closer look.

28:58.780 --> 28:59.580
It's indeed quite good.

29:00.300 --> 29:00.740
How about this,

29:01.100 --> 29:02.500
I'll arrange a time with the landlord

29:02.500 --> 29:03.179
to check it out.

29:04.820 --> 29:05.379
No, no.

29:05.820 --> 29:07.100
I'll go by myself.

29:07.580 --> 29:08.699
I don't want to waste your time.

29:09.500 --> 29:10.179
I'm on a different schedule.

29:10.580 --> 29:12.060
I work nights.

29:12.580 --> 29:14.459
Besides, it's safer

29:14.780 --> 29:15.659
to have a lawyer

29:15.780 --> 29:16.740
with you for the lease.

29:17.740 --> 29:19.219
Okay, thank you.

29:19.659 --> 29:20.179
No problem.

29:22.300 --> 29:22.899
This way, please.

29:23.820 --> 29:24.260
Please come in.

29:24.540 --> 29:25.219
Okay, thank you.

29:25.300 --> 29:25.820
Thank you.

29:28.260 --> 29:29.699
The security in this complex is pretty good.

29:30.139 --> 29:31.379
The security guards seem very responsible.

29:32.020 --> 29:33.340
However, the rent for this house

29:33.340 --> 29:34.459
is more expensive than

29:34.459 --> 29:35.139
the other complexes around.

29:35.820 --> 29:36.540
Maybe we should wait a bit longer

29:36.699 --> 29:37.419
and we might find one

29:37.419 --> 29:38.419
with better value for money.

29:39.219 --> 29:40.219
It's an emergency situation.

29:40.459 --> 29:41.260
We can only

29:41.260 --> 29:42.179
give up on it.

29:42.619 --> 29:43.659
The one we're looking at

29:43.659 --> 29:44.740
is a small high-rise apartment.

29:46.020 --> 29:46.659
The layout,

29:46.659 --> 29:47.659
lighting, and everything else

29:47.659 --> 29:48.340
are pretty good.

29:48.740 --> 29:50.260
The condition of the house

29:50.260 --> 29:50.859
looks pretty good from the pictures.

29:51.300 --> 29:52.419
And it's a direct lease from the landlord.

29:52.939 --> 29:54.340
If the landlord is nice,

29:54.619 --> 29:55.340
then it would be perfect.

29:57.219 --> 29:57.619
How's the sunlight

29:57.619 --> 29:58.699
in the morning?

29:59.179 --> 29:59.939
See for yourself.

30:02.780 --> 30:03.500
What about the soundproofing?

30:04.179 --> 30:04.820
Listen for yourself.

30:06.939 --> 30:07.980
So, how much is the rent

30:07.980 --> 30:08.859
for this place?

30:09.459 --> 30:10.580
It's all written online.

30:10.939 --> 30:11.619
No bargaining?

30:13.740 --> 30:15.060
That's about it. Let's go.

30:16.820 --> 30:17.300
Thanks.

30:23.060 --> 30:24.300
Why does this landlord sound

30:24.300 --> 30:25.459
like I owe him money?

30:26.540 --> 30:27.500
Maybe you owe him

30:27.500 --> 30:28.939
a potential romantic partner.

30:30.020 --> 30:30.500
Look.

30:33.459 --> 30:34.060
Sir,

30:34.379 --> 30:35.060
does this apartment

30:35.060 --> 30:35.980
require a deposit and three months' rent?

30:36.580 --> 30:37.980
Of course, beauty.

30:38.459 --> 30:40.260
Can we see it this afternoon?

30:40.500 --> 30:41.219
Anytime.

30:41.980 --> 30:43.179
Miss, my apartment

30:43.179 --> 30:44.500
is for single women only.

30:44.540 --> 30:45.060
I'm afraid

30:45.060 --> 30:46.020
young couples like you

30:46.020 --> 30:47.100
would get too intimate.

30:47.340 --> 30:48.540
But you just told me this morning

30:48.540 --> 30:49.540
that you fit the bill.

30:49.619 --> 30:51.139
What young couples and getting too intimate?

30:51.859 --> 30:53.139
You're just making excuses

30:53.139 --> 30:54.020
because you're hiding something.

31:00.419 --> 31:01.060
Sorry,

31:01.419 --> 31:02.340
I just got out of a relationship this morning.

31:05.419 --> 31:06.540
When you're single again,

31:06.619 --> 31:07.100
come back and rent,

31:07.379 --> 31:08.179
I'll keep it for you.

31:09.179 --> 31:10.820
Thank you. Maybe next life.

31:11.740 --> 31:12.899
All right, let's go.

31:15.939 --> 31:17.379
Xu Huaisong has been acting

31:17.379 --> 31:18.219
strangely these days.

31:18.740 --> 31:19.740
He's been

31:19.740 --> 31:20.740
unusually nice to me.

31:21.300 --> 31:22.859
Yesterday, he just talked more.

31:23.659 --> 31:24.540
Today, even his words

31:24.540 --> 31:25.340
are out of character.

31:26.780 --> 31:27.540
Lawyer Xu,

31:28.659 --> 31:30.300
may I ask you something?

31:31.260 --> 31:31.699
Okay.

31:33.020 --> 31:33.899
Are you...

31:36.980 --> 31:38.060
I mean,

31:38.740 --> 31:39.899
is it possible that

31:41.419 --> 31:42.379
you are possessed?

31:48.820 --> 31:50.020
I'm sorry.

31:50.260 --> 31:51.060
I shouldn't have asked.

31:51.899 --> 31:52.619
I was just saying.

31:55.219 --> 31:56.659
This house is not suitable.

31:57.260 --> 31:58.100
Let's look at another one.

31:59.619 --> 32:00.260
Another one.

32:13.060 --> 32:14.379
This is near Heng University.

32:15.580 --> 32:16.260
We're passing by.

32:16.659 --> 32:17.419
Would you like to take a look?

32:18.980 --> 32:19.659
No need.

32:20.100 --> 32:20.899
Let's just go

32:20.899 --> 32:21.699
to the next one.

32:36.780 --> 32:37.419
Lawyer Xu,

32:37.419 --> 32:38.419
I'm really sorry.

32:38.740 --> 32:39.820
My phone died earlier,

32:39.820 --> 32:40.540
so I didn't get a chance

32:40.540 --> 32:41.300
to let you know I was safe.

33:00.580 --> 33:01.379
I... I...

33:03.020 --> 33:04.379
Am I that obvious?

33:04.780 --> 33:05.340
No.

33:06.580 --> 33:07.340
I'm the one who's craving it.

33:13.659 --> 33:14.219
Hello.

33:15.459 --> 33:16.699
Double bean milk tea.

33:16.980 --> 33:17.459
Thank you.

33:18.260 --> 33:19.459
Full sugar, no tea base.

33:19.459 --> 33:20.300
Milk replaced with soy milk.

33:20.300 --> 33:21.419
Only red bean, no mung bean.

33:22.740 --> 33:23.699
It's really you, girl.

33:24.300 --> 33:25.419
Your taste hasn't changed over the years.

33:26.780 --> 33:27.899
Do you still remember me, boss?

33:28.300 --> 33:30.100
I don't remember the person,

33:30.419 --> 33:31.379
but I remember your taste.

33:32.260 --> 33:33.500
This guy looks a bit unfamiliar.

33:34.020 --> 33:34.899
Why isn't it the one from before?

33:37.419 --> 33:38.500
You must have the wrong person, boss.

33:38.699 --> 33:39.500
How could that be?

33:39.780 --> 33:40.820
The one before

33:40.820 --> 33:41.899
became a celebrity later on.

33:42.300 --> 33:43.020
He's been coming by every now and then

33:43.020 --> 33:44.060
to support my business.

33:44.139 --> 33:45.060
His crew orders a lot of milk tea,

33:45.060 --> 33:45.980
hundreds of cups at a time.

33:47.580 --> 33:49.179
He came by recently too,

33:49.580 --> 33:50.619
and ordered the same flavor as yours.

33:50.859 --> 33:52.340
But they only ordered one cup.

33:52.899 --> 33:53.820
You are so beautiful.

33:53.820 --> 33:54.980
You should go and act in movies with him.

33:55.060 --> 33:55.980
You will definitely be popular.

34:01.139 --> 34:02.379
Sir, here's your lemon tea.

34:02.699 --> 34:03.500
It's a bit sour.

34:03.899 --> 34:04.580
No, no.

34:04.820 --> 34:05.980
Just added some lemon.

34:06.219 --> 34:06.899
Not too sour.

34:07.780 --> 34:08.500
Please enjoy.

34:08.980 --> 34:09.500
Thank you.

34:33.940 --> 34:36.060
I didn't expect it to be so difficult to find a house.

34:38.299 --> 34:39.219
Take it easy.

34:40.139 --> 34:40.779
The worst thing

34:40.779 --> 34:42.060
in negotiating a contract is haste.

34:42.980 --> 34:44.900
It's easy to be tricked if you're in a hurry.

34:48.500 --> 34:49.139
Lawyer Xu,

34:50.100 --> 34:50.779
maybe

34:51.299 --> 34:52.739
I have to bother you for a few more days.

34:53.420 --> 34:53.940
It doesn't matter.

34:54.460 --> 34:55.420
You must be tired from looking at houses.

34:56.259 --> 34:57.060
Have a seat on the sofa.

35:16.819 --> 35:18.420
Come on, play with me.

35:20.940 --> 35:21.580
Mimi.

35:25.779 --> 35:26.420
Watch your hand.

35:27.739 --> 35:28.339
Lawyer Xu,

35:28.779 --> 35:30.060
I don't know its name yet.

35:31.219 --> 35:31.739
Tiffany.

35:33.540 --> 35:33.860
Right.

35:34.219 --> 35:35.500
It's a foreign cat.

35:36.500 --> 35:37.259
When in China, do as the Chinese do.

35:37.259 --> 35:37.900
You can also give it

35:37.900 --> 35:38.819
a Chinese name.

35:39.860 --> 35:40.500
I'll name it.

35:47.179 --> 35:48.540
You're so lively.

35:49.179 --> 35:50.219
how about we call it Pipi?

35:50.779 --> 35:51.699
Let's be a healthy,

35:51.980 --> 35:53.339
robust little kitty,

35:53.339 --> 35:53.980
okay?

35:54.699 --> 35:55.219
Pipi,

35:55.699 --> 35:56.420
purr purr.

35:56.940 --> 35:57.940
Looks like it agrees.

35:59.420 --> 36:00.100
Pipi,

36:00.100 --> 36:00.500
come here.

36:05.460 --> 36:06.060
No rush.

36:08.779 --> 36:09.380
Lawyer Xu,

36:09.860 --> 36:11.179
I didn't expect that after all these years,

36:11.179 --> 36:12.339
you still like orange cats the most.

36:14.980 --> 36:16.860
Is the fact that I like orange cats

36:19.580 --> 36:21.020
reported in the news again?

36:24.819 --> 36:25.460
No.

36:26.860 --> 36:28.860
I... I heard it from Lawyer Liu.

36:30.980 --> 36:32.460
Did I tell Lawyer Liu about this?

36:34.380 --> 36:34.940
I think so.

36:34.940 --> 36:35.860
Maybe you don't remember.

36:41.699 --> 36:43.380
Lawyer Xu, are you hungry?

36:44.380 --> 36:44.860
Okay.

36:45.739 --> 36:47.659
I'll go make you some food.

36:53.580 --> 36:55.219
No, we need to find a house.

36:55.659 --> 36:56.739
Keep looking for a house.

36:56.940 --> 36:57.860
Keep looking for a house.

36:57.860 --> 36:58.339
I can't stay here.

37:11.540 --> 37:13.060
This restaurant has a great reputation.

37:13.299 --> 37:13.980
I've reserved a table.

37:14.100 --> 37:14.980
I'll take you there tomorrow.

37:17.380 --> 37:18.139
Do you know

37:18.139 --> 37:19.179
you're getting promoted

37:19.940 --> 37:21.020
and want to thank me in advance?

37:23.500 --> 37:24.339
What promotion?

37:31.299 --> 37:32.219
Who are you

37:32.219 --> 37:32.900
talking to?

37:33.699 --> 37:35.219
We're talking about work.

37:36.219 --> 37:37.219
Why did you come out

37:37.219 --> 37:37.980
without drying your hair?

37:38.380 --> 37:39.060
I'll do it later.

37:42.659 --> 37:43.659
Creative Director,

37:44.179 --> 37:46.299
annual salary plus stock options, how is it?

37:47.380 --> 37:48.380
I'm with you

37:48.380 --> 37:49.699
not for promotions or raises.

37:50.259 --> 37:51.420
And my current job

37:51.420 --> 37:52.500
is also steadily advancing.

37:52.980 --> 37:54.060
I don't want to rely on you.

38:02.139 --> 38:02.779
You've been coming home

38:02.779 --> 38:03.779
coming home lately.

38:04.500 --> 38:05.179
You never

38:05.179 --> 38:06.619
spent the night outside before.

38:08.819 --> 38:09.659
Baby,

38:14.339 --> 38:15.779
I've been busy lately.

38:15.779 --> 38:16.779
Don't be mad at me.

38:18.779 --> 38:19.860
But things are different now.

38:20.339 --> 38:21.139
I got promoted.

38:22.500 --> 38:23.179
When?

38:23.779 --> 38:24.659
Just recently.

38:25.980 --> 38:26.900
I was planning to wait

38:26.900 --> 38:28.380
until the official announcement

38:28.699 --> 38:29.299
until the new personnel appointment

38:29.299 --> 38:30.179
to give you a surprise.

38:31.659 --> 38:33.380
Mr. Gao of your company values you.

38:35.060 --> 38:36.380
About that.

38:37.940 --> 38:38.619
It's not in vain

38:38.619 --> 38:39.940
that I've worked so many nights.

38:45.020 --> 38:45.540
Enough.

38:50.860 --> 38:51.860
Congratulations, Chuan.

38:57.259 --> 38:58.100
I'm going to dry my hair.

39:16.619 --> 39:17.500
We can eat now.

39:39.500 --> 39:40.819
I accidentally fell asleep.

39:41.100 --> 39:42.020
It seems that you're too tired.

39:43.380 --> 39:44.659
Wash your hands and have dinner.

39:44.940 --> 39:45.779
Go to bed early tonight.

40:10.699 --> 40:12.860
I bought it on my way to the mall last night.

40:15.739 --> 40:16.659
For me?

40:18.699 --> 40:19.819
Didn't you forget to bring a hair tie?

40:22.380 --> 40:22.699
Yeah.

40:23.500 --> 40:24.380
This is too expensive.

40:30.100 --> 40:31.540
You can spend money on it,

40:32.179 --> 40:33.339
but I can't?

40:36.699 --> 40:38.299
I have a legitimate reason

40:38.299 --> 40:39.380
to give you a gift.

40:41.020 --> 40:42.060
What's your reason?

40:53.940 --> 40:54.580
Then...

40:56.819 --> 40:58.659
Happy New Year in advance.

41:00.739 --> 41:01.460
Is it reasonable enough?

41:07.819 --> 41:08.339
Thank you.

41:12.580 --> 41:13.259
Put it on first.

41:13.500 --> 41:14.380
It's more convenient to eat.

42:33.980 --> 42:35.219
Hello, here's your express delivery.

42:42.940 --> 42:44.100
Hello, here's your express delivery.

42:44.659 --> 42:46.659
Express delivery? Are you sure it's for me?

42:48.900 --> 42:51.060
Is it Xu Huaisong?

42:51.540 --> 42:51.940
Yes.

42:52.699 --> 42:53.940
This is a same-city express delivery.

42:53.940 --> 42:54.739
The client requested

42:54.739 --> 42:55.219
it must be delivered

42:55.219 --> 42:56.060
tonight,

42:56.540 --> 42:58.100
and you must personally sign for it.

42:58.460 --> 42:59.900
It's a surprise for you.

43:00.619 --> 43:01.420
What surprise?

43:03.100 --> 43:04.020
Surprise?

43:35.580 --> 43:36.699
Miss Ruan, please.

43:37.179 --> 43:37.860
This house

43:38.100 --> 43:39.500
is a rare large apartment

43:39.500 --> 43:40.980
within the second ring road.

43:42.779 --> 43:44.259
The furniture and appliances

43:44.460 --> 43:46.259
are all top international brands,

43:46.500 --> 43:47.699
and well-maintained.

43:47.940 --> 43:48.900
Each of the three bedrooms

43:49.139 --> 43:50.540
has its own bathroom.

43:50.779 --> 43:52.139
The value for money is unbeatable.

43:53.540 --> 43:54.779
How much is the rent?

43:55.420 --> 43:55.980
4,000 yuan.

43:56.739 --> 43:57.259
What?

44:00.940 --> 44:01.819
If you think

44:01.819 --> 44:03.139
the price is too high,

44:03.139 --> 44:03.940
we can negotiate.

44:06.139 --> 44:07.100
Negotiate?

44:07.860 --> 44:08.699
As far as I know,

44:08.819 --> 44:09.619
houses of the same size and type

44:09.619 --> 44:11.139
in this community

44:11.500 --> 44:12.819
rent for around

44:12.819 --> 44:13.819
18,000 yuan.

44:16.540 --> 44:18.659
The landlord of this house

44:18.659 --> 44:20.259
is abroad for a long time.

44:20.460 --> 44:21.619
If these appliances

44:22.020 --> 44:23.339
are not used for a long time,

44:23.339 --> 44:24.020
they will be easy to break down.

44:24.299 --> 44:25.779
So the tenant is like

44:25.940 --> 44:26.940
maintaining the house.

44:27.819 --> 44:28.699
That's why the price

44:28.699 --> 44:29.500
is lower.

44:30.259 --> 44:30.860
I see.

44:31.619 --> 44:32.699
Thank you.

44:32.860 --> 44:33.779
I'll get in touch

44:33.779 --> 44:34.540
if I need anything.

44:36.900 --> 44:37.500
Miss Ruan.

44:37.580 --> 44:37.980
Thank you.

44:37.980 --> 44:39.179
If you have any concerns,

44:39.179 --> 44:40.219
just let us know.

44:40.819 --> 44:41.500
No worries, Miss Ruan.

44:41.819 --> 44:42.420
Take your time.

44:42.819 --> 44:43.619
Bro,

44:44.420 --> 44:45.179
the agent said

44:45.299 --> 44:46.739
the client didn't like any of them.

44:48.179 --> 44:49.219
What kind of houses did you pick?

44:52.179 --> 44:52.779
Bro, look,

44:53.540 --> 44:55.259
whether it's the landscaping, renovation,

44:55.460 --> 44:57.219
height, lighting, or ventilation,

44:57.219 --> 44:57.980
I carefully selected

44:57.980 --> 44:59.020
every single one

44:59.500 --> 45:00.339
according to your instructions.

45:00.339 --> 45:01.179
They're all

45:02.139 --> 45:02.699
pretty good.

45:02.900 --> 45:04.540
So, how much did you quote?

45:05.020 --> 45:05.699
4,000.

45:06.580 --> 45:07.739
I really don't get it.

45:08.060 --> 45:08.940
How can someone

45:08.940 --> 45:10.460
not be tempted by this price?

45:10.819 --> 45:11.819
What's wrong with people these days?

45:12.179 --> 45:13.299
Do they treat money like dirt?

45:15.779 --> 45:18.540
You must have worked really hard.

45:19.420 --> 45:20.219
Not at all, not at all.

45:20.219 --> 45:21.259
Bro, it's my duty.

45:22.139 --> 45:22.779
I should do it.
